<h2>T<font size=-1>HE</font> I<font size=-1>MAGE</font> <font size=-1>OF</font> M<font size=-1>AN</font>.<br></h2>
<p> By George Mosse. <br>
<i>OUP; 232 pages; $25.</i><br>
</p><br>
<a href="6jb151.html">Jacket Copy</a><br>
<p><b>Biography</p></b>

George L. Mosse is Bascom-Weinstein Professor of History Emeritus at the
University of Wisconsin Madison and is Koebner Professor of History
Emeritus at the Hebrew University in Jerusalem. He is the author of a number
of books including Fallen Soldiers: Reshaping the Memory of the World Wars.<p><a href="http://www.economist.com/index.html"><i>The Economist</i> Home Page</a> &nbsp; - &nbsp; <a href="http://www.economist.com/cgi-bin/search_form.cgi?832374000,rev">Search</a>
