<p><b><a href="1rt2/review.htm">Anti-Enlightenment visionary</a></b><br>

<font size=1>BLAKE. By Peter Ackroyd.</font></p>

<p><b><a href="1rt3/review.htm">Enlightenment luminary</a></b><br>

<font size=1>THE LIFE OF ADAM SMITH. By Ian Ross.</font></p>

<p><b><a href="1rt4/review.htm">Microsoft</a></b><br>

