<html><head><title>Extract</title></head><body background="http://www.economist.com/review/images/rback.gif" bgcolor="#FFFFFF"><img src="http://www.economist.com/review/images/rlogo.gif" alt="review logo"><table cellpadding=0 cellspacing=0 border=0><tr><td valign=bottom align=left><img src="http://www.economist.com/review/images/instrap.gif"></td><td><h2>FISHER'S FACE</h2><p>By Jan Morris. <i>Viking; 242 pages; &#163;16</i></h2><p><a href="1jb1-4.htm">Jacket copy</a> - <a href="1bt1-4.htm">Biography</a></p><p><b>No extract available</b><br><br><a href="http://www.economist.com/review/">Review Index</a> &nbsp; -  &nbsp  <a href="http://www.economist.com/">The Economist</a></td></tr></table></body></html>
