<DOCHDR>
http://www.economist.com:80/review/rev1/1rt10/1ex10-2.htm 199.173.162.110 19970113235837 text/html 3832
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 13-Jan-97 23:54:48 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 25-Jul-96 18:55:28 GMT
