<DOCHDR>
http://www.economist.com:80/review/rev1/1rt1/1jb1-3.htm 199.173.162.110 19970114045320 text/html 3620
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Tuesday, 14-Jan-97 04:49:09 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 25-Jul-96 18:55:28 GMT
Content-length: 3434
