<DOCNO>WT21-B40-203</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA029-000316-B041-140</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.economist.com:80/review/rev1/1rt2/1jb2-1.htm 199.173.162.110 19970114050916 text/html 3105
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Tuesday, 14-Jan-97 05:05:34 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 25-Jul-96 18:55:29 GMT
Content-length: 2919
