<p align=center>{<a href="nont2.html">single column version</a>}<br>{<a href="http://www.economist.com/review/archive.html">Review Archive</a>}</p><br>
<table cellpadding=0 cellspacing=0><tr><td width=60 valign=top align=left><img src="http://www.economist.com/review/images/instrap.gif"></td><td valign=top width=300>
<p><font size="+1"><b><a href="2rt1/review.html">Murder in mind</a></b></font><br>
<font size=-1>The Dark Room &nbsp; <i>By Minette Walters. </i>
 -- An Image to Die For &nbsp; <i>By Mike Phillips. </i>
