<h2>F<font size=-1>ENCE</font> J<font size=-1>UMPERS</font><br>
</h2>
<p>By Robert Leuci.<br><i>St Martin's Press; 338 pages; $22.95.</i></p>
<p><a href="2jb1-2.html">Jacket Copy</a></p><p><b>Biography</b></p>
<p>ROBERT LEUCI is a former New York policeman whose experiences as an undercover detective during the Knapp Investigation of the seventies were told in Robert Daley's bestselling book, Prince of the City, and the movie made from it. Leuci subsequently has written several books of his own, the most recent being the crime novel Double Edge. He lives in Rhode Island, near Providence.<p>
<p>
