<h2>S<font size=-1>HE</font> P<font size=-1>LAYS</font> <font size=-1>WITH</font> <font size=-1>THE</font> D<font size=-1>ARKNESS</font><br>
</h2>
<p>By Zakes Mda. <br><i>Vivlia Publishers; 207 pages; 36.99 rand</i>.</p>
<p><a href="2bt2-1.html">Biography</a></p><p><b>Jacket Copy</b></p>
<p>In this second novel Zakes Mda weaves a story of love and magic in the misty mountains, and of betrayal in the city. He is a humane writer, and a sensitive and inventive storyteller with the eye for absurdity and tenderness. In the twins of Ha Samane - especially in Dikosha, the dancing girl who never ages - he has created characters who will live in our memory for many years to come. She Plays with the Darkness is a first-rate literary experience.<p>
<p>
