<h2>S<font size=-1>HE</font> P<font size=-1>LAYS</font> <font size=-1>WITH</font> <font size=-1>THE</font> D<font size=-1>ARKNESS</font><br>
</h2>
<p>By Zakes Mda. <br><i>Vivlia Publishers; 207 pages; 36.99 rand</i>.</p>
<p><a href="2jb2-1.html">Jacket Copy</a></p><p><b>Biography</b></p>
<p>Zakes Mda is the pen-name of Professor Zanemvula Kizito Gatyeni Mda, the well-known playwright, painter and filmmaker. As an academic he has worked as the National University of Lesotho, Yale University, University of Vermont, University of the Witwatersrand, and has presented many papers and held workshops in many other institutions in Africa and Europe. He currently lives in Johannesburg where he works fulltime as a writer, painter and director of both theatre and film.<p>
