<h2>M<font size=-1>EGATRENDS</font> A<font size=-1>SIA</font><br>
</h2>
<p>By John Naisbitt<br><i>Nicholas Brealey. 304 pages; 15.99. Simon &amp; Schuster; $24</i></p>
<p><a href="2jb4-1.html">Jacket Copy</a></p><p><b>Biography</b></p>
<p>John Naisbitt, bestselling author of Megatrends, which sold 8 million copies worldwide and accurately predicted 10 major patterns of change which would shape the world in the 1980s, is recognized as one of the world's top social forecasters. He has been a visiting fellow at Harvard, a visiting professor at Moscow State University and is Distinguished International Fellow of the Institute of Strategic and International Studies (ISIS), Malaysia. He is a renowned international speaker and is also the author of Global Paradox (Nicholas Brealey, 1994).<p>
<p>
<p>
