<p>Anthony King has been Professor of Government at the University of Essex since 1969. He analyses the Gallup Poll for the Daily Telegraph. Since 1994 he has been a member of the Nolan Committee on Standards in Public Life.<p>
<p>Both authors will be familiar to many for their numerous appearances on television election-night broadcasts.<p>
<p>
