http://www.economist.com:80/review/rev5/rv1/review.html 199.173.162.110 19970113184044 text/html 11583
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 13-Jan-97 18:36:59 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 08-Aug-96 14:04:07 GMT
