<p><b>Biography</p></b>

Dan Balz is a national political correspondent and former National Editor of the Wcrshington Post. Ronald Brownstein is a national political correspondent for the Los Angeles limes and writes its "Washington Outlook" column.<p><a href="http://www.economist.com/index.html"><i>The Economist</i> Home Page</a> &nbsp; - &nbsp; <a href="http://www.economist.com/cgi-bin/search_form.cgi?829954800,rev">Search</a>
