<p> By James Patterson. <br>
<i>Oxford University Press; 880 pages; $35</i><br>
</p><br>
<a href="5jb121.html">Jacket Copy</a><br>
<p><b>Biography</p></b>

James T. Patterson is Ford Foundation Professor of History at Brown
University.<p><a href="http://www.economist.com/index.html"><i>The Economist</i> Home Page</a> &nbsp; - &nbsp; <a href="http://www.economist.com/cgi-bin/search_form.cgi?829954800,rev">Search</a>
