<i>Newmarket Press</i>; <i>352 pages; $24.95</i>. 
<br>Published in Britain as Y<font size=-1>ITZHAK </font>R<font size=-1>ABIN</font>: S<font size=-1>OLDIER</font> <font size=-1>OF</font> P<font size=-1>EACE</font>.
