<i>Norton; 352 pages; $25</i>. 
<br>Published in Britain as T<font size=-1>HE</font> R<font size=-1>EAL</font> P<font size=-1>RICE</font> <font size=-1>OF</font> J<font size=-1>APANESE</font> M<font size=-1>ONEY</font>. 
