<p><b>Biography</p></b>

Robert Neild is a retired professor of economics and a Fellow of Trinity
College, Cambridge University. During a career which included spells in India,
Papua New Guinea, Sweden, Switzerland, the United States and Whitehall,
working on many different subjects, he found himself always drawn back to his
