<html><head><title>The Economist Review</title></head>
<body background="http://www.economist.com/review/images/rback.gif" bgcolor="#FFFFFF">
<table width=100% cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0><tr><td valign=top align=left><img src="http://www.economist.com/review/rev8/logo8.gif" alt="review logo">
</td><td align=center valign=top><img src="http://www.economist.com/review/rev8/8gr.gif" alt="graphic"></td></tr></table>
<p align=center>{<a href="http://www.economist.com/review/rev8/single.html">single column version</a>}<br>
