</p><br>
<a href="3jb37.html">Jacket Copy</a><br>
<p><b>Biography</p></b>
<p>
</p><p><p>The Author</p>
</p><p>Roy Godson, a professor of government at Georgetown University, founded the Consortium for the Study of Intelligence in 1979. He has been a consultant to the National Security Council, the President's Foreign Intelligence Advisory Board, and other agencies in the United States concerned with intelligence. <br>
</p>
