<p><b>Biography</p></b>
<p>
</p><p>
</p><p>HARRISON KINNEY worked as a reporter for The New Yorker from 1949 to 1954. The author of a previous book of nonfiction, a novel, and two children's books, he lives in Carmel, New York. <br>
</p>
